    <briefdescription>
<para>Reader side of the lock-free SPMC ring buffer. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Multiple readers can exist per topic (up to MAX_SUBSCRIBERS). Each reader claims a slot via <ref refid="classconduit_1_1internal_1_1RingBufferReader_1a6a64780945bc4c45f368847fc54e2bcc" kindref="member">claim_slot()</ref>, then reads messages independently. If the writer laps a reader, the reader detects the overwrite via sequence number validation and skips ahead.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="classconduit_1_1internal_1_1RingBufferWriter" kindref="compound">RingBufferWriter</ref> </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
